episodes.title: War and Peace
episodes.plot: With a difference of opinion related to the ongoing war, Dr. Homi Bhabha and Dr. Vikram Sarabhai look back at the time when they first met each other.

episodes.title: It's Like Gravity
episodes.plot: As Homi and Vikram's friendship grows, an unexpected roadblock leads them to meet a few people who will alter the course of their lives.

episodes.title: The Greater Good
episodes.plot: Homi and Vikram set out on their individual paths in hopes to achieve their dreams.

episodes.title: A Tryst with Destiny
episodes.plot: Emerging as an Independent country, Homi and Vikram share their vision for the country. A new face comes to light while a threat lurks in the shadow.

episodes.title: The Outsider
episodes.plot: Homi and Vikram face a backlash both at personal and professional life.

episodes.title: The Democratic Process
episodes.plot: Their ideas and ambitions are challenged by a fierce rebellion. They must choose a path that they deem fit.

episodes.title: We are at War
episodes.plot: While India gets ready to take its first step in Nuclear science, another dream gets into acceleration, but an impending war threatens to tear it all down.

episodes.title: A New Dawn
episodes.plot: As the country starts to heal the wound from the war, the great men come together for one final showdown to do the impossible.
